          This sample showcases the row selection capability of SfDataGrid. SfDataGrid control provides an interactive support for selecting rows in different mode with smooth and ease manner by SelectionUnit property as Row. It supports to select a specific row or group of rows programmatically or by Mouse and Keyboard interactions by SelectionMode property. This property provides options like Single, Multiple, Extended and None.
